      "description": "Honest value and a practical opportunity for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone seeking affordable transportation, a project, or a dependable parts candidate. It offers a straightforward way into ownership at a budget-friendly price, backed by clear, transparent representation from a trusted seller. If you know what you\u2019re looking for, this could be a smart buy.",
