      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants basic transportation, a starter project, or a handy runabout. It has the kind of character you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle, and for the right buyer, it could be a great little opportunity without spending big money. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, this one is well worth a look.",
